setTranslatedNames] = useState(allahNames); useEffect(() => { const translateNames = async () => { try { const responses = await Promise.all(allahNames.map(name => axios.post('http://localhost:5000/translate', { text: name.meaning, target_lang: 'tr', // Translate to Turkish }) )); const translations = responses.map(response => response.data.text); const translatedNamesWithMeanings = allahNames.map((name, index) => ({ ...name, translatedMeaning: translations[index], })); setTranslatedNames(translatedNamesWithMeanings); } catch (error) { console.error('Translation Error:', error); } }; translateNames(); }, []); return (
{translatedNames.map((name, index) => (

{name.frame} - {name.name}

{name.translatedMeaning ? name.translatedMeaning : name.meaning}

))}
); }; export default AllahIsimleri;
